'''HotGen, Ltd.''' is a toy and [[video game developer]] based in [[London]]. They work for [[Jakks Pacific]] and help develop [[handheld TV game]]s. In late 2016 the company became a wholly owned subsidiary of Skyrocket Toys, a California-based toy design company.
