'''Ya Sang''' or Yaa Sang ({{lang-th|ยาสั่ง}}) is said to be a form of [[black magic]] performed in Thailand's northeast, [[Isan]].  It is based on traditional knowledge of plant poisons, some causing stomach ailments, physical pain, and intoxication, leading to death.

